      <title>由于美联储停滞不前，印度尼西亚将“暂时”维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/indonesia-holds-rate-to-preserve-rupiah-amid-lingering-risks</link>
